(the guiltier Sang Yun feels.)

1566
01:05:23.000 --> 01:05:24.000
(What should I do?)

1567
01:05:24.000 --> 01:05:26.139
Hey, get up already!

1568
01:05:26.139 --> 01:05:28.139
(I guess I should just dunk my face in the snow now.)

1569
