1591
01:07:03.100 --> 01:07:05.239
(a wave of guilt surges up in Sang Yun's heart.)

1592
01:07:05.469 --> 01:07:07.440
I don't think my cheekbones are moving. Are they moving?

1593
01:07:07.440 --> 01:07:08.440
(Is my face paralyzed now?)

1594
01:07:12.210 --> 01:07:14.279
Wait, I don't think I can move my jaw.

1595
01:07:14.949 --> 01:07:16.480
(That's my cheekbone.)

1596
01:07:16.480 --> 01:07:17.480
My jaw isn't moving.

1597
01:07:19.279 --> 01:07:21.279
(I'm sorry, guys.)

